snippet.title: FEE3 2023: Drums of War by Parrhesia
snippet.description:
Fire Emblem: Drums of War is a 22-chapter hack built on FE8's bones, with a story exploring the themes of loyalty, love and loss, and gameplay that looks to iterate on the GBAFE formula without re-inventing it.

Featured art by the immensely skilled CrimeanRoyalKnight.

https://feuniverse.us/t/fe8-fire-emblem-drums-of-war-v-2-complete-22-chapter-campaign/16368
